[P1 Press L1+Select To Disable See Through Walls]
author=Code Master, Liquid
description=Be careful, make sure you can walk on the current level you're on at full speed before disabling this code, or you might get stuck!
patch=1,EE,D033CB82,extended,0000FEFE
patch=1,EE,20125AA0,extended,8FA80078

[P1 Press L1+Select To Enable See Through Walls]
author=Code Master, Liquid
description=You will be able to walk through some objects/walls. If you are going up on stairs with this code on, keep Pressing Triangle until you jump higher & walk forward and land higher up. Repeat this process until you are at the top. If you can't move very fast, walk back to the stairs & play with the Triangle jump button until you can jump 'high enough' to be on the current level your on.
patch=1,EE,D033CB82,extended,0000FBFE
patch=1,EE,20125AA0,extended,24080000

